    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a dream to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, super reliable, and totally ready for many more adventures with a new owner! It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being broken in just right while still looking great in the driveway. If you're looking for a dependable car that won't let you down and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
