    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The engine maintains exceptional compression, benefiting from a recent VANOS system refresh and a subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Power is delivered through a factory M-Variable differential, providing excellent traction out of corners. The chassis has been enhanced with Bilstein dampers for improved damping rates without sacrificing street compliance. It presents as a highly capable driver\u2019s car with crisp throttle response from the individual throttle bodies and a tight, communicative steering rack. Minor aesthetic wear is present, but the mechanical vitals are sorted for the next enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
