    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been a fantastic car for me and is still in really solid shape, running smoothly and looking great. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, making it a perfect, reliable choice for its next owner. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how nicely it handles! Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat! \u2728",
      "price": 29500.0,
