    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through its individual throttle bodies. The VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. Equipped with a 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock, it offers exceptional mechanical feedback. The suspension retains its sharp turn-in thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While it shows minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust and the compression across all cylinders is within spec. A driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
